            <title>[LU-112] In installing RPM, notice suggests visiting sun.com for support</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-112</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;h2&gt;&lt;a name=&quot;Toreproduce&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;To reproduce&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;checkout Lustre source git://git.whamcloud.com/fs/lustre-release.git, branch b1_8&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Follow the manual (downloaded from lustre.org) on installing Lustre 1.8 from source.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Build rpms,&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;rpm -ivh lustre-modules-1.8.5.54-2.6.18_194.32.1.el5.lustre18_201103040823.x86_64.rpm&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The message below is returned:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;



&lt;p&gt;Congratulations on finishing your Lustre installation!  To register&lt;br/&gt;
your copy of Lustre and find out more about Lustre Support, Service,&lt;br/&gt;
and Training offerings please visit&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.sun.com/software/products/lustre/lustre_reg.jsp&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://www.sun.com/software/products/lustre/lustre_reg.jsp&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;h2&gt;&lt;a name=&quot;Expectedresult&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Expected result&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;s/sun.com/whamcloud.com/&lt;/p&gt;</description>
